21#ifndef GCC_CXX_PRETTY_PRINT_H
22#define GCC_CXX_PRETTY_PRINT_H
23
24#include "c-family/c-pretty-print.h"
25
26enum cxx_pretty_printer_flags
27{
28 /* Ask for a qualified-id. */
29 pp_cxx_flag_default_argument = 1 << pp_c_flag_last_bit
30};
31
32struct cxx_pretty_printer : c_pretty_printer
33{
34 cxx_pretty_printer ();
35
36 void constant (tree);
37 void id_expression (tree);
38 void primary_expression (tree);
39 void postfix_expression (tree);
40 void unary_expression (tree);
41 void multiplicative_expression (tree);
42 void conditional_expression (tree);
43 void assignment_expression (tree);
44 void expression (tree);
45 void type_id (tree);
46 void statement (tree);
47 void declaration (tree);
48 void declaration_specifiers (tree);
49 void simple_type_specifier (tree);
50 void function_specifier (tree);
51 void declarator (tree);
52 void direct_declarator (tree);
53 void abstract_declarator (tree);
54 void direct_abstract_declarator (tree);
55
56 /* This is the enclosing scope of the entity being pretty-printed. */
57 tree enclosing_scope;
58};
59
60#define pp_cxx_cv_qualifier_seq(PP, T) \
61 pp_c_type_qualifier_list (PP, T)
62#define pp_cxx_cv_qualifiers(PP, CV, FT) \
63 pp_c_cv_qualifiers (PP, CV, FT)
64
65#define pp_cxx_whitespace(PP) pp_c_whitespace (PP)
66#define pp_cxx_left_paren(PP) pp_c_left_paren (PP)
67#define pp_cxx_right_paren(PP) pp_c_right_paren (PP)
68#define pp_cxx_left_brace(PP) pp_c_left_brace (PP)
69#define pp_cxx_right_brace(PP) pp_c_right_brace (PP)
70#define pp_cxx_left_bracket(PP) pp_c_left_bracket (PP)
71#define pp_cxx_right_bracket(PP) pp_c_right_bracket (PP)
72#define pp_cxx_dot(PP) pp_c_dot (PP)
73#define pp_cxx_ampersand(PP) pp_c_ampersand (PP)
74#define pp_cxx_star(PP) pp_c_star (PP)
75#define pp_cxx_arrow(PP) pp_c_arrow (PP)
76#define pp_cxx_semicolon(PP) pp_c_semicolon (PP)
77#define pp_cxx_complement(PP) pp_c_complement (PP)
78
79#define pp_cxx_ws_string(PP, I) pp_c_ws_string (PP, I)
80#define pp_cxx_identifier(PP, I) pp_c_identifier (PP, I)
81#define pp_cxx_tree_identifier(PP, T) \
82 pp_c_tree_identifier (PP, T)
83
84void pp_cxx_begin_template_argument_list (cxx_pretty_printer *);
85void pp_cxx_end_template_argument_list (cxx_pretty_printer *);
86void pp_cxx_colon_colon (cxx_pretty_printer *);
87void pp_cxx_separate_with (cxx_pretty_printer *, int);
88
89void pp_cxx_canonical_template_parameter (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
90void pp_cxx_trait_expression (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
91void pp_cxx_va_arg_expression (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
92void pp_cxx_offsetof_expression (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
93void pp_cxx_addressof_expression (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
94void pp_cxx_userdef_literal (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
95void pp_cxx_requires_clause (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
96void pp_cxx_requires_expr (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
97void pp_cxx_simple_requirement (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
98void pp_cxx_type_requirement (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
99void pp_cxx_compound_requirement (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
100void pp_cxx_nested_requirement (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
101void pp_cxx_predicate_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
102void pp_cxx_expression_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
103void pp_cxx_type_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
104void pp_cxx_implicit_conversion_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
105void pp_cxx_argument_deduction_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
106void pp_cxx_exception_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
107void pp_cxx_parameterized_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
108void pp_cxx_conjunction (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
109void pp_cxx_disjunction (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
110void pp_cxx_constraint (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
111void pp_cxx_constrained_type_spec (cxx_pretty_printer *, tree);
